    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 80.16,
      "start_time": 79.45,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 9,
      "text": "Good man."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 86.77,
      "start_time": 80.17,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 10,
      "text": "Switching between meum platforms is always crazy and um good to hear you."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 87.04,
      "start_time": 86.84,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "Hi."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 89.17,
      "start_time": 87.72,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 12,
      "text": "Yeah, thanks for following up."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 91.42,
      "start_time": 89.37,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 13,
      "text": "Um So"
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 99.19,
      "start_time": 93.21,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 14,
      "text": "uh at the end of the day, at this moment, we're gonna have to hold with our market reports."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 100.11,
      "start_time": 99.63,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 15,
      "text": "Ok?"
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 105.91,
      "start_time": 100.17,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 16,
      "text": "Um And let me, let me just give you some kind of insight on where we are and what's going on."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 123.99,
      "start_time": 106.53,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 17,
      "text": "Um Larry and I have done a full audit of all of our data subscriptions and um we've done kind of some justification to the leadership team about our subscriptions, what we're paying for."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 127.28,
      "start_time": 124,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 18,
      "text": "And as, as you might expect, we, we have a lot of data subscriptions."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 133.08,
      "start_time": 127.86,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 19,
      "text": "Um and we're, we're paying a significant amount of money in licenses, licensing, et cetera."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 144.95,
      "start_time": 133.92,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 20,
      "text": "And um essentially when we took the cost to the, the executive leadership team, we because it isn't budgeted, we couldn't get an approval for it."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 146.01,
      "start_time": 145.66,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 21,
      "text": "Got it."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 158.3,
      "start_time": 146.83,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 22,
      "text": "So, so all that to say it's not the price, it's not the quality it's not what you have, it's just, we can't come up with the money right now which all ties back to."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 161.34,
      "start_time": 158.31,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 23,
      "text": "We're just in a super difficult market from a development standpoint."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 163.17,
      "start_time": 161.86,
      "recording_attendee_id": "91ab96d1-f49c-4b69-ac6f-0250720152ee",
      "order_number": 24,
      "text": "Yeah, that makes sense."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 164.07,
      "start_time": 163.7,
      "recording_attendee_id": "91ab96d1-f49c-4b69-ac6f-0250720152ee",
      "order_number": 25,
      "text": "So, when, I"
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 167.8,
      "start_time": 165.11,
      "recording_attendee_id": "91ab96d1-f49c-4b69-ac6f-0250720152ee",
      "order_number": 26,
      "text": "guess when, when do you, when will you rebut David?"
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 170.38,
      "start_time": 167.81,
      "recording_attendee_id": "91ab96d1-f49c-4b69-ac6f-0250720152ee",
      "order_number": 27,
      "text": "I'm assuming, end of the year starting in September."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 171.55,
      "start_time": 171.38,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 28,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 178.74,
      "start_time": 171.56,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 29,
      "text": "September, October, I think September is when you start to budget and, um, you know, we'll absolutely."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 187.18,
      "start_time": 179,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 30,
      "text": "So, so at the end of the day, you guys are becoming a critical piece of our, our business process, there's no question about that."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 196.65,
      "start_time": 188.13,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 31,
      "text": "Um It's uh it's just, you know, at, at this moment in time, we can solve our critical need with your market reports."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 200.73,
      "start_time": 197.24,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 32,
      "text": "And so, um that's where we're gonna have to stay."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 215.5,
      "start_time": 201.49,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 33,
      "text": "Uh But, you know, again, you guys have been super helpful, super flexible and um you know, not moving forward with a much bigger opportunity is, is no reflection on you."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 217.66,
      "start_time": 215.51,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 34,
      "text": "It's a reflection on us in the market at the moment."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 219.94,
      "start_time": 218.31,
      "recording_attendee_id": "91ab96d1-f49c-4b69-ac6f-0250720152ee",
      "order_number": 35,
      "text": "Yeah, that, that checks out."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 221.42,
      "start_time": 220.18,
      "recording_attendee_id": "91ab96d1-f49c-4b69-ac6f-0250720152ee",
      "order_number": 36,
      "text": "It's no problem for us."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 228.06,
      "start_time": 221.43,
      "recording_attendee_id": "91ab96d1-f49c-4b69-ac6f-0250720152ee",
      "order_number": 37,
      "text": "Um And honestly with, with what we're working on, it might be uh it's gonna be a better fit even come October."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 231.54,
      "start_time": 228.43,
      "recording_attendee_id": "91ab96d1-f49c-4b69-ac6f-0250720152ee",
      "order_number": 38,
      "text": "Uh there's gonna be all more data pieces."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 237.54,
      "start_time": 231.55,
      "recording_attendee_id": "91ab96d1-f49c-4b69-ac6f-0250720152ee",
      "order_number": 39,
      "text": "Um our trends reporting and our research reporting will be out in a matter of weeks."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 243.08,
      "start_time": 238.18,
      "recording_attendee_id": "91ab96d1-f49c-4b69-ac6f-0250720152ee",
      "order_number": 40,
      "text": "Uh And so why don't we, why don't we just plan to uh to revisit when it makes more sense for you."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 245.62,
      "start_time": 244.34,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 41,
      "text": "Yeah, absolutely."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 254.8,
      "start_time": 245.63,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 42,
      "text": "And, and on that note, um you know, as, as you're starting to release additional products and additional functionality, keep me up to speed."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 268.08,
      "start_time": 255.45,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 43,
      "text": "Um Because the other thing that there is a potential to occur is we've got to, um we've got one data subscription that is grossly expensive."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 277.41,
      "start_time": 268.84,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
      "order_number": 44,
      "text": "Um And if we can drop that data subscription, it may give us a little bit of flexibility in pulling something different in."
    },
    {
      "id": "c6fa2789-9c9d-4ea3-88d1-f2e7c17e8f93",
      "recording_id": "e8d39184-761b-43e0-bca6-15cd0e024569",
      "end_time": 283.54,
      "start_time": 278.18,
      "recording_attendee_id": "5eae8038-04c5-4667-8bb1-ad6ab3f61654",
